%% 3.2.6 Edit Route — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin or Staff
    participant UI as UI (Bus Routes)
    participant RC as Controller (BusRouteController)
    participant RS as Service (BusRouteService)
    participant Repo as Repository (BusRoute BusRouteStation)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>RC: GET /api/BusRoute/Get/{id} — load stops order
    RC-->>UI: route + stations

    Actor->>UI: Reorder / remove / add stops — Save
    alt Empty StationIds
        UI-->>Actor: Inline warning — FE
    else Valid list
        UI->>RC: PUT /api/BusRoute/Update/{id} BusRouteUpdateDto
        RC->>RS: UpdateBusRouteAsync
        RS->>RS: ValidateStationIds min 1 no dup
        RS->>Repo: Replace BusRouteStation rows OrderIndex 1..n
        Repo->>DB: DELETE old + INSERT new
        RC-->>UI: 200
    end
